<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Jul1925"><font color="red">1 July 1925</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I have been working all day amid noise and workmen till now on Shem. My sight is momentarily impaired &hellip; I shall therefore stop now, have the last corrections made and send off the piece and lie down &hellip; I want this Shem piece and the river piece to be as finished as I can make them. I am doubtful as to their succession </div>
